{"tid":1632914,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"我有少少野想講","createTime":"2019-10-07T01:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:37:18.000Z","uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b98048930be2f07f232238c528670da4e6c04ea","tid":1632914,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:07:42.000Z","msg":"由9月開始，寶寶已經驚發完夢後返歸途中俾狗咬，所以寶寶如果當日唔做和理非而帶上gear，都會同朋友講好個日邊度近就會暫時存放個位手足既倉，個倉可以係locker / 公司 / 租房 / 朋友家 / 或者極少人會行入既草叢度，目的都係等自己走個陣安全，等下次發夢再拎出黎用。<br />\n呢個方法試左好多次，適合人數少既組別去參考。<br />\n雖然每個地方都唔同，但係發夢發得多，都識到唔同地區既手足，單身既手足，識多一個戰友互相照應，點都安全過孤身作戰⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n一個無連登acc嘅黑衣人<br />\n<br />\n107 晚上一定要出黎各區開花，但要留返命仔至108以後... <br />\n108 全港攬炒，無地鐵，路又便秘，啲港豬一定返唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://t.me/hkposter777/11442\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkposter777%2F11442&h=9abf9185&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c26a75ad170fbc48ea97b058c8c36944a4bd6ccd","tid":1632914,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a6zU1ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa6zU1ee.jpg&h=2daa73b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iyAUgNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiyAUgNA.jpg&h=28273dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n善心打破0回覆"},{"pid":"23907f52dd8f5734afcce84c11b1e54d9ff66548","tid":1632914,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awtq7UL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fawtq7UL.png&h=2a4ed527&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}